Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Throbs of a New Darkness"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other news, some new ruins have been discovered in the Atlantic Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say it is older than anything we've discovered so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's said to be part of an ancient civilization from long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-OWWW~!!\N -OWWW~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more careful!\N Ya walked right into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right back {\i1}at{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Insector Haga!\N -Dinosaur Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya can't be here for Battle City since it ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're ya doin' in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing much, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyhow, what are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to get those God Cards!\NNo matter what I have to do, I will get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ain't about to be outdone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I have ta trade all my rare cards, I'm gonna add those God Cards to my collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Whoa! Outta da way!\N -Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Move it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are ya standin' there for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are ye Sir Dinosaur Ryuzaki and Sir Insector Haga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do ya want somethin' wit' us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I come to claim thine souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words are pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DUEL!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing all the way up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just doing some thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner, did you bring\N the God Cards today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's head to the art museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You didn't tell the others about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too painful to bid farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm fine with just\N you seeing me off, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YUGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OIIIII!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were acting odd this morning and then you just rushed off by yourself, so we hurried over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's harsh, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going by yourself like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're about to start a new journey, Other Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'd be sad if\N we couldn't bid you farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, no matter how apart we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our hearts will always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is that palette everyone keeps talking about, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really does look just like Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come at last...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once I show these three God Cards to the Palette,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...my lost memories will be opened, along with a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And {\b0}then{\b1} what will happen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer is {\b0}here{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stone tablet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I.... feel a different and powerful energy interfering...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you regain your memory or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the slate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone's Duel Disk break or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't look like they're being controlled...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, all the data on the different Monsters is stored in Kaiba Corporation's main computer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's head over to Kaiba Corporation\N and see if they know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, this is Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you're saying it suddenly\N appeared in your back yard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our computers are functioning normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monsters are all over the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Those guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Ryuzaki and Haga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, what are you doing at a time like this, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The omen has begun~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon this world's gonna be destroyed~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Omen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by, "this world will be destroyed?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this creepy feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about these guys. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us about the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the rumors that the Solid Vision System is the cause of all this really true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system is working fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assure you, there is no relation to this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, then what exactly is causing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have President Kaiba comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President Kaiba is currently in America on important business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be holding a press conference later this evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't take this as a proper response!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even speaking the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really here, President Kaiba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so crowded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other news, many sightings of Duel Monsters Solid Vision holograms have been spotted around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As of current, there is no real explanation for these events and the panic they are causing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this event is all around the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Domino City\N isn't the only one affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now we take you live to a press conference with Kaiba Corporation's president in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our system has absolutely nothing to do with the crisis that has been occurring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Immediately after these sightings were reported, we shut down all of our systems to test them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}During the time the systems were down, Monsters were still appearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, something other than our system is causing the Monsters to materialize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal? If it's not Kaiba's system causing this, then what is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this all be related to what\N happened at the palette today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've been thinking it's a possibility as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, a strong power disrupted the palette and my memory returning to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after, these Monsters started coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what puzzles me most is what Haga and Ryuzaki said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The omens have begun~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soon this world's gonna be destroyed~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, those guys were acting funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did they mean by "the world will be destroyed"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GRANDPA!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, gramps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-Yugi, I'm sorry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The....the God Cards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great War God... Obelisk...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great War God Obelisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just Obelisk...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra and Osiris, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only Millennium Item Possessors should be able to Summon the three God Cards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just who could have-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the forbidden door is opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the light of Orichalcos shall punish this sinful world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are The Musketeers of Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Musketeers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were the ones who stole the God Cards!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, we have taken these cards, O Great Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These guys know about my other self?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We issue a challenge to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want the cards back,\N come to the unfinished building!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Musketeers of Doma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Safety first"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. We have been\N awaiting thy arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Yugi Mutou...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, should I address thee as "Nameless Pharaoh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Are you in cahoots with those motorcycle-riding bastards from before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thou be correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Gurimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the Musketeers of Doma,\N as well as Master Raphael's servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Will thee accept my Duel challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. But before that, I have one thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God Cards are cards that won't allow anyone but the chosen ones to wield them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to use them, God's anger will consume you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to use them or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will have to confirm that with your own two eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting. I'll accept this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become our offering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-DUEL!!\N -LET'S DUEL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Magnet Warrior Beta in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I set one reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't attack on the first turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh.\N Allow us to test your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is now my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he really has the God Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he does use them, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Yugi's the King of Duelists now, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't lose that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Marauding Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I activate Marauding Captain's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lets me Special Summon another Monster of Level 4 or below.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Demon Tamer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In just one turn, two Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Yugi, the time has now come for me to show you our {\i1}true{\i0} power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold! A Magic Card born from the very darkness itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This age old power has\N become {\i1}our{\i0} power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall seal my enemy within a sacred barrier of divine justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as this boundary exists on the field, all distractions are forcefully removed so we can focus entirely on the Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the Duel's outcome has been determined,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not a single being shall be granted passage within this barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And vice versa, neither I nor thee shall be permitted to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one capable\N of exiting this bound...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is none other than\N the winner of the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the loser's soul shall forever be sealed within the sacred boundary for all eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is able to\N control the Dark Games?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as we remain within this boundary, the power of the Millennium Items are nullified!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Barrier of Orichalcos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not the power of the Millennium Items,\N but a whole different power...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only just begun showing you the true power of the Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns my Monsters into Dark Monsters and raises their Attack Power by 500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Marauding Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Magnet Warrior Beta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card's effect starts when one of my Monsters are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the cost of 1000 Life Points, I can Special Summon a Four-Star Monster from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet Warrior Gamma in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought I got rid of all your Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owww~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard... ever since that boundary was activated, his character changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All his Monsters became Dark Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And most importantly, when he said, "the loser's soul will be sealed within the boundary," what did he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your subordinate all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael, does this Yugi\N really stand a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's defeated by him here, that means the Nameless Pharaoh isn't worthy of being our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing more, nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that leaves Katsuya Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Seto Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must obtain all three of their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our plan must not fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Magnet Warrior Alpha in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, my Trap Card activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden Soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card activates when the opponent successfully Summons a Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lets me Summon a Dark-Attribute Monster from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Executioner Makuyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to activate a Magic Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shallow Grave, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:19:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lets both players Summon a Monster from their Graveyards in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster I'm reviving is... Magnet Warrior Beta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha, Beta, Gamma! Now all three of the\N Magnet Warriors have gathered!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come! Join together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet Valkyrian!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have no Monster you can Summon in your Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the rumors are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Gurimo still has that card...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Magnet Valkyrian!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Life Points fell significantly from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the King of Duelists for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm about to Summon a much more {\i1}powerful{\i0} Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Magnet Warrior Valkyrian's Attack Points are higher than almost all Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But mine is different from the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to act cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only Monsters with more than 3500 Attack Points are the God Cards, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}wouldn't{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The card I'm about to play\N is the God Card, The Great War God Obelisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card Resurrection of the Dead\N to revive Marauding Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! If you're unable to handle God, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice all 3 of my Monsters in play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, appear before us in your greatest form!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GREAT WAR GOD, OBELISK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Attack went up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk became a Dark Monster...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you said those who aren't the "chosen ones" couldn't play the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I {\i1}did{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anything{\i0} is possible within the holy bounds of the Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Barrier of Orichalcos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's doesn't even have a Millennium Item, yet this Duelist can control God...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What in the world {\i1}is{\i0} he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:22:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(121,115)}PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi faces off against the God Card under Doma's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.11,0:23:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is there a way for Yugi to defeat the God Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even worse, the Barrier of Orichalcos's effect powers up the opponents Monsters greatly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the loser of this Duel really have their soul taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the opponent is acting kind of weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.76,0:23:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Barrier of Orichalcos"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
